Value: Oventus Medical Limited, a medical device company, develops and commercializes oral appliances for the treatment of obstructive sleep apnoea (OSA) and snoring in Australia, Canada, and the United States. The company offers O2Vent Optima, a 3D-printed nylon oral appliance for OSA patients; and ExVent, a valve accessory that fits into the open airway of the O2Vent Optima device. The company was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Indooroopilly, Australia.
